flowchart TD
    Start([System Issue Detected]) --> CheckLog{Check Server Logs}
    
    CheckLog -->|Error 500| DBCheck{Is DB Online?}
    CheckLog -->|Error 404| Routing[Check Router Config]
    CheckLog -->|Timeout| Network((Network Outage))
    
    DBCheck -->|Yes| AppBug[Investigate App Bug]
    DBCheck -->|No| RestartDB>Restart Database]
    
    RestartDB --> Verify[Verify Connection]
    Verify -->|Fails| Escalate[[Escalate to DBA]]
    Verify -->|Succeeds| Resolve{{Resolve Incident}}
    
    AppBug --> Resolve
    Routing --> Resolve
    Network --> Resolve
